    "Html": "<p>Hi,</p>\r\n<p>Take into account that in <strong>MVVM presentation pattern</strong>, the View Model is responsible for updating the View. The controller&rsquo;s responsibility is to interact with your repository and updating view model's values. Also cab be shared between multiple view models.</p>\r\n<p>In Prism documentation MSDN, <a href=\"http://msdn.microsoft.com/en-us/library/ff921146(v=PandP.40).aspx\">Appendix B: Patterns in Prism Library</a> covers all the patterns used in the library.</p>\r\n<p>Thanks,</p>\r\n<p>Miguel Bronzovic<br /><a href=\"http://blogs.southworks.net/mbronzovic\">http://blogs.southworks.net/mbronzovic</a></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>",
